<p>I have written this code to input two array of characters <code>a</code> and <code>b</code> of size <code>5</code> each.</p>  <p>When I give the input :</p>  <pre><code>abcde abcde </code></pre>  <p>the output <code>b[2]</code> should be <code>c</code> but it is giving as <code>b</code>. </p>  <pre><code>#include &lt;stdio.h&gt;  using namespace std;  int main(){     char a[5], b[5];    int i;    for(i = 0; i &lt; 5; i++){        scanf("%c", a + i);    }     for(i = 0; i &lt; 5; i++){        scanf("%c", b + i);    }      printf("%c", b[2]); } </code></pre>